          alongside all Hipo community.
        </div>
        <div class='text-purple3 mx-auto my-8'>Shape GRAM&apos;s future with $HPO!</div>
        <img src='/images/rocket.webp' class='mx-auto h-80 object-cover mix-blend-screen' alt='Rocket Illustration' />
      </div>

      <div class='relative z-10 mb-24 overflow-x-clip px-16'>
        <img
          src='/images/diamond.svg'
          class='absolute top-8 right-2 -z-10 h-24 -rotate-12 object-contain opacity-20'
          alt='Diamond Decoration'
        />
        <div class='mb-12 text-3xl font-bold'>How to Buy HPO</div>
        <div class='mb-12 flex w-full flex-col gap-8 text-left sm:grid sm:grid-flow-row sm:grid-cols-2'>
          <div class='flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4'>
            <div
              class='from-purple1 to-purple2 flex h-14 w-14 place-content-center items-center rounded-2xl bg-radial text-3xl'
            >
              01
            </div>
            <div class=''>Get a wallet supporting TON.</div>
          </div>

          <div class='flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4'>
            <div
              class='from-purple1 to-purple2 flex h-14 w-14 place-content-center items-center rounded-2xl bg-radial text-3xl'
            >
              02
            </div>
            <div class=''>Ensure you have enough GRAM for your desired $HPO purchase.</div>
          </div>

          <div class='flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4'>
            <div
              class='from-purple1 to-purple2 flex h-14 w-14 place-content-center items-center rounded-2xl bg-radial text-3xl'
            >
              03
            </div>
            <div class=''>Head to the STON.fi DEX and connect your TON wallet.</div>
          </div>

          <div class='flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4'>
            <div
              class='from-purple1 to-purple2 flex h-14 w-14 place-content-center items-center rounded-2xl bg-radial text-3xl'
            >
              04
            </div>
            <div class=''>Swap your GRAM for $HPO, and receive $HPO in your wallet instantly.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='mb-12 flex w-full flex-col items-center'>
          <iframe
            class='aspect-video h-full w-full rounded-md'
            src='https://youtube.com/embed/ZHAlS4wystU?feature=share'
            title='YouTube video player'
            allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture'
