      <div class='mb-8'>
        <div class='text-4xl font-bold'>Tokenomics</div>
        <img src='/images/tokenomics.svg' class='my-8 w-full' alt='HPO Tokenomics Chart' />
      </div>

      <div class='mb-32 px-8 text-2xl sm:mx-24'>
        Each category in $HPO tokenomics is strategically designed to fuel Hipo&apos;s growth.
        <a
          href='https://docs.hipo.finance/hipo-tokens/hipo-governance-token-hpo'
          class='text-purple3'
          target='_blank'
          rel='noopener noreferrer'
        >
          Learn more!
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class='mx-8 mb-32 flex flex-col gap-16'>
