            <div class='bg-brush inline-block bg-contain bg-bottom bg-no-repeat pb-2 text-left text-2xl font-bold'>
              Proven, Not Just a Plan
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='text-left text-lg'>
            Hipo has been live on TON mainnet since October 30, 2023, with $HPO as its governance token—a solid
            foundation built over a year.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='flex max-w-200 flex-col items-start gap-8 md:grid md:grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-2'>
